      "span_text": "It was shown in [CITATION_1] that every ϕ ∈ S m induces a bounded composition operator on each of the spaces H 2 m,β , satisfying a \"one-variable style\" norm estimate, in particular an estimate which depends only on the value of ϕ at 0."
